1268
01:27:43.364 --> 01:27:44.664
Grazie, signore.

1269
01:27:46.214 --> 01:27:47.064
Grazie.

1270
01:27:51.072 --> 01:27:52.072
Oh, salve.

1271
01:27:55.075 --> 01:27:56.875
Benvenuta, classe del '55.

1272
